text: Puerto Rico Highway 798 (PR-798) is a road located between the municipalities of Caguas, Puerto Rico, and San Juan, and it corresponds to an original segment of the historic Carretera Central. La Concepción Bridge is located on this route. With ==Major intersections== ==See also== *List of highways numbered 798 ==References== 798 Category:Caguas, Puerto Rico
